<script>
    window.App.IndexController.reopen({
        actions: {
            submitAction: function(){
                this.set("isSubmitting", true );
                $('#emberForm').submit();
                return true;
            },
            createnewAction: function(){
                this.set("isSubmitting", true );
                document.getElementById('outcome').value = "new";
                $('#emberForm').submit();
            }
        }
    });
</script>

<script type="text/x-handlebars" data-template-name="index">
    
    {{#sc-container}}

        {{#sc-buttons}}

            {{#sc-button action='createnewAction'}}

            {{/sc-button}}
        {{/sc-buttons}}
        
        <input id='outcome' name='outcome' type='hidden' value="">

        {{#sc-overlay active=isSubmitting}}
            {{sc-loading center=true}}
        {{/sc-overlay}}

    {{/sc-container}}
    
</script>
